faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"from 房署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就 本 規 則 而 言，申 請 一 次 過 特 別 編 配 安 排 下 租 住 公 屋 的<br />\r\n人 員 如 因 下 述 情 況 確 實 遇 到 困 難 或 家 庭 發 生 重 大 轉<br />\r\n變，房屋署會特別考慮以下情況的租住公屋申請－<br />\r\n( i ) 經法庭裁定破產；<br />\r\n( ii ) 陷入經濟困境以致需領 取綜合社會保障援助金；<br />\r\n( ii i) 家 庭 環 境 逆 轉，例 如 離 婚、家 庭 經 濟 支 柱 身 故 等 ；<br />\r\n( i v) 家庭收入銳減，以致難以償還按揭貸款；或<br />\r\n( v ) 家庭面對健康或個人問題，但嚴重程度不足以令<br />\r\n他們符合接受體恤安置的資格。"},{"pid":"f0e6321ab313a9c8f2a26147ae8abc4199b8bc7d","tid":1690891,"uid":277869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"470897a064a0e9fab1d62302b14a56ec51a549c7","tid":1690891,"uid":55010,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"用左你個名一世人就冇左房屋福利，唔好比佢利用。 完"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"唉好難講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ea11a5c860fa2a28e28c7386d0ce0af2daed1c","tid":1690891,"uid":4258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f0e6321ab313a9c8f2a26147ae8abc4199b8bc7d","tid":1690891,"uid":277869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"470897a064a0e9fab1d62302b14a56ec51a549c7","tid":1690891,"uid":55010,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"用左你個名一世人就冇左房屋福利，唔好比佢利用。 完"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"唉好難講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"咁就咪上嚟問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217c7f0709e50972cea51d649eba6ccb9ff8354e","tid":1690891,"uid":8511,